race.comment: WRITTEN FAME (2) has produced good figures all prep, the latest effort a game third over 1350m at Ipswich five weeks ago. Has his share of weight but should be right there at the business end again. VACILLATION (9) returned in fine order at Beaudesert recently, showing intent from barrier rise then battling on well to be beaten narrowly. Has won second-up before so he should hold that form. NEXT PAY RUN (11) wasn't too far off the winner when resuming at Grafton last start. In the mix from a perfect draw. Race depth seemingly tapers off quite sharply after this trio in terms of winning chances. PRANCING WITH FIRE (7) first up next best.
